	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">Nymm's Sigil Games Online Visit</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Nymm</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Aug 16, 2004, 15:08</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=Nymm%27s%20Sigil%20Games%20Online%20Visit&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Fevents%2Farticle_4.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
